Package: oeis.tools
Title: OEIS Toolkit for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Enrique", "Pérez Herrero", 
           email = "energycode.org@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A focused R toolkit for working with OEIS integer sequences: 
    fetch metadata, parse b-files, and plot sequence values quickly.
    This package provides an object-oriented interface to the Online 
    Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences (OEIS) at https://oeis.org.
